### Test SSE Streaming - Real Progress Reporting
### This file tests the real-time SSE streaming with actual progress updates

### 1. Simple Query - Should complete in ~5-10s with smooth progress
POST https://localhost:7189/api/v2/agent/process/stream
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv VITE_TEST_TOKEN}}

{
  "question": "Show me all users",
  "connectionId": "{{$dotenv CONNECTION_ID}}"
}

###

### 2. Complex Query - Should show all stages including RAG and SQL generation
POST https://localhost:7189/api/v2/agent/process/stream
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv VITE_TEST_TOKEN}}

{
  "question": "Compare total revenue by region for the last 3 months",
  "connectionId": "{{$dotenv CONNECTION_ID}}"
}

###

### 3. Query with SQL Error - Should show CORRECTING stage
POST https://localhost:7189/api/v2/agent/process/stream
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv VITE_TEST_TOKEN}}

{
  "question": "Show me users with invalid_column",
  "connectionId": "{{$dotenv CONNECTION_ID}}"
}

###

### 4. Forbidden Query - Should stop at CLASSIFYING stage
POST https://localhost:7189/api/v2/agent/process/stream
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv VITE_TEST_TOKEN}}

{
  "question": "DROP TABLE users",
  "connectionId": "{{$dotenv CONNECTION_ID}}"
}

###

### Expected SSE Events Timeline:
###
### Event 1 (0-500ms):
### event: stage_update
### data: {"stage":"VALIDATING","message":"Validating...","progress":0.05}
###
### Event 2 (500ms-2s):
### event: stage_update
### data: {"stage":"CLASSIFYING","message":"Analyzing intent...","progress":0.10}
###
### Event 3 (2-5s):
### event: stage_update
### data: {"stage":"SCHEMA_RETRIEVAL","message":"Loading schema...","progress":0.20}
###
### Event 4 (5-7s):
### event: stage_update
### data: {"stage":"SCHEMA_RETRIEVAL","message":"Finding relevant tables...","progress":0.35}
###
### Event 5 (7-20s):
### event: stage_update
### data: {"stage":"SQL_GENERATION","message":"Generating SQL...","progress":0.50}
###
### Event 6 (20-21s):
### event: stage_update
### data: {"stage":"SQL_VALIDATION","message":"Validating SQL...","progress":0.65}
###
### Event 7 (21-25s):
### event: stage_update
### data: {"stage":"EXECUTING","message":"Executing SQL...","progress":0.75}
###
### Event 8 (if error - 25-28s):
### event: stage_update
### data: {"stage":"CORRECTING","message":"Auto-correcting SQL...","progress":0.78}
###
### Event 9 (28-30s):
### event: stage_update
### data: {"stage":"BUILDING_RESPONSE","message":"Building response...","progress":0.90}
###
### Event 10 (30s):
### event: stage_update
### data: {"stage":"COMPLETED","message":"Processing complete!","progress":1.0}
###
### Event 11 (30s):
### event: result
### data: {"success":true,"answer":"...","sql":"...","data":[...]}
